      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RAPID RITA (1) comes off an average run last start when fifth at this track over 622m behind Deep Space (36.68) in a Grade 5. Was in the money the start prior. Speedy beginner who should be in the action early off the inside. Looks the one to beat on her best form. CALL YOUR BLUFF (2) found the frame for the second consecutive time when narrowly beaten into third last time out (29.93) over 520m at Wentworth Park. With a good start should be able to take advantage of the low draw. Can feature with the right run. LOCO KADE (3) had been racing well with a Grade 5 win three back then placed next time before missing the frame latest at Wentworth Park. Well placed here and should do much better. BOY BANDIT (8) will be hard to beat despite making his debut at this circuit.",
